PN is proposed by Dr. Petri in 1962 when he developed information flow model for computer operation system (David and Alla, 1994) . At present, PN is extensively applied to performance analysis and control research for discrete event dynamic system. As a system model, PN is dynamic and concurrent. In PN standard graphic presentation, the sign ''O" indicates place and the sign ''|" or pane indicates transition (Yuan, 1998) . 